item.p:
The {internal_error,...,{ unrecognized_type,...}}
            error occurring for a SET type when compiling with options
            [ber_bin,optimize,der] is now corrected.

The decoder can now detect if there are unexpected bytes 
            remaining when all components of a sequence are decoded.
            The decoder will then return {error,{asn1{unexpected,Bytes}}}

